                           <p class="dl__slide__caption">
                            <a class="dl__slide__summary" data-ylk="ll2:amp-bon;aid:aol_com_127=bsd%3Aentertainment;cpos:16;slk:Don Lemon erupts on Sen.                              Lemon didn't hold back on Scott, the only Black Republican in the Senate, for making the "shameful" comparison.
                            </a>

                             'Youre not helping'
                            </a>
                           </p>
                          </div>

                             Biden on Thursday signed the American Rescue Plan into law, the first major legislative achievement of his presidency. It passed with zero Republican votes.
